author: wrowe
msg: We need to map any external references to the -old- Announcement links
into the new schema.  This gets ugly with respect to external links,
and the fact that /dist/httpd/ isn't necessarily the RewriteBase on
an arbitrary patch such as /pub/asf/httpd/ if that's how the mirror
decided to map us.  So this is the best I could come up with, with the
help of four of the finest regex/mod_rewrite minds ... feel free to
prove us wrong, that there is a reliable way to do this better across
flavors of mod_rewrite from Apache 1.3 through 2.2, shout :)
